  theme: dark
---
flowchart TD
    Start([User Clicks Rock/Paper/Scissors]) --> CheckStart{hasStarted?}
    CheckStart -->|No| ClearLogs[Clear all logs]
    CheckStart -->|Yes| SkipClear[Skip clear]
    ClearLogs --> SetStart[Set hasStarted = true]
    SkipClear --> GenRandom[Generate random number]
    SetStart --> GenRandom
    GenRandom --> RandCheck{Random value?}
    RandCheck -->|0-0.33| UmairRock[Umair = rock]
    RandCheck -->|0.33-0.67| UmairPaper[Umair = paper]
    RandCheck -->|0.67-1| UmairScissors[Umair = scissors]
    UmairRock --> LogUmair[Log Umair's move]
    UmairPaper --> LogUmair
    UmairScissors --> LogUmair
    LogUmair --> UserChoice[Set userChoice from input]
    UserChoice --> LogUser[Log user's move]
    LogUser --> CompareGame{Compare moves}
    CompareGame -->|Same move| ResultTie[Result: Try Again]
    CompareGame -->|Umair beats user| ResultUmair[Result: Umair Wins]
    CompareGame -->|User beats Umair| ResultUser[Result: You Win]
    ResultTie --> UpdateScore{Update scores}
    ResultUmair --> UpdateScore
    ResultUser --> UpdateScore
    UpdateScore -->|User Win| IncUser[Increment youScore]
    UpdateScore -->|Umair Win| IncUmair[Increment umairScore]
    UpdateScore -->|Tie| NoScore[No score change]
    IncUser --> LogResult[Log result]
    IncUmair --> LogResult
    NoScore --> LogResult
    LogResult --> End([Game round complete])
    
    Reset[Reset button clicked] --> ResetScores[Set both scores to 0]
    ResetScores --> ResetLogs[Clear all logs]
    ResetLogs --> ResetStart[Set hasStarted = false]
    ResetStart --> ResetEnd([Ready for new game])